column5: Located in the Far North Dallas area (zip code 75252), a lively neighborhood keeping everything close to your fingertips: Retail, Restaurants, Grocery stores, Pubs, Nail Salons, Dog Grooming, and much more. You are sure to enjoy! Available from 5/25/2017 to 5/28/2017.
column8: 1 Bed/Bath entire apartment located near UT Dallas
